%% OpenVINO Model Server - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OVMSHTTP as OVMS REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP plaintext
    participant OVMSgRPC as OVMS gRPC<br/>8085/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant OpenVINO as OpenVINO Runtime<br/>In-process C++ API
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: Model Inference via KServe (REST)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>RBACProxy: Forward (TLS)<br/>Port 8443
    RBACProxy->>OVMSHTTP: Forward (plaintext)<br/>Port 8080
    OVMSHTTP->>OpenVINO: Execute inference<br/>C++ API (in-process)
    OpenVINO-->>OVMSHTTP: Inference result
    OVMSHTTP-->>RBACProxy: JSON Response
    RBACProxy-->>Gateway: Response (TLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: OpenAI-compatible Chat Completions
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v3/v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token + API Key
    Gateway->>RBACProxy: Forward (TLS)
    RBACProxy->>OVMSHTTP: Forward (plaintext)
    OVMSHTTP->>OpenVINO: MediaPipe LLM graph<br/>Continuous batching + streaming
    OpenVINO-->>OVMSHTTP: Streaming tokens
    OVMSHTTP-->>RBACProxy: SSE stream
    RBACProxy-->>Gateway: Stream
    Gateway-->>Client: SSE Response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 3: gRPC Inference (Internal)
    Client->>OVMSgRPC: ModelInfer RPC<br/>Insecure credentials
    OVMSgRPC->>OpenVINO: Execute inference<br/>C++ API (in-process)
    OpenVINO-->>OVMSgRPC: Inference result
    OVMSgRPC-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 4: Model Loading from Storage
    OVMSHTTP->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / GCP SA / Azure Keys
    Storage-->>OVMSHTTP: Model files

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 5: HuggingFace Model Pull
    OVMSHTTP->>HFHub: Pull model (--pull mode)<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN (optional)
    HFHub-->>OVMSHTTP: Model artifacts + quantization

    Note over Prom,OVMSHTTP: Flow 6: Metrics Collection
    Prom->>OVMSHTTP: GET /metrics<br/>No auth
    OVMSHTTP-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
